{"tid":161061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普炮轟中國　「未能控制北韓核發展」","createTime":"2017-03-18T09:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T03:51:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc115c3073e29fcaea9bf3623b9463516a53a67","tid":161061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/mobile/bknint-20170317214730393-0317_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170317214730393-0317_17011_001.html&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b5217662\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/mobile/bknint-20170317214730393-0317_17011_001.html</a><br />\n03月17日(五) 21:47   <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/photo/bknint-20170317214730393-0317_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170317222219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170317214730393-0317_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170317222219&h=53fcf69a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">特朗普在twitter炮轟中國。（美聯社／互聯網圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n正當美國國務卿蒂勒森訪問南韓，親訪兩韓非軍事區，更表明不會再容忍北韓之際，美國總統特朗普亦「加入戰團」，出言炮轟中國在抑制北韓核發展一事上未有盡力。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普在twitter上發文，指北韓的行為惡劣，多年來持續玩弄美國，更指中國在此事務上一直做得太少，實在沒有太大幫忙。 <br />\n<br />\n早前，蒂勒森到訪南韓首爾後表明，美國對北韓的戰略耐性已耗盡；又強硬表明雖不願有軍事矛盾，但如果朝方加劇軍事威脅超過美方底線，對北韓採取軍事行動將是「其中一個選擇」。他周六將前往最後一站中國。<br />\n<br />\n全方位追擊特朗普狂潮　即上「狂人入主白宮」專頁"},{"pid":"5238978f8de8b9c35f19f200a44bcbf2a13835ac","tid":161061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935930eaa8c5cd475a4f02386080f6eb9cbcfc9b","tid":161061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply